        "text": "=Score this job against my profile.\n\nMY PROFILE:\nPrimary Roles: {{ $('🎯 Agent: Profile Generation').first().json.output.primaryRoles }}\nCore Skills: {{ $('🎯 Agent: Profile Generation').first().json.output.coreSkills }}\nSeniority: {{ $('🎯 Agent: Profile Generation').first().json.output.seniority }}\nExpected Salary: {{ $('🎯 Agent: Profile Generation').first().json.output.expectedSalary }}\nExclusions: {{ $('🎯 Agent: Profile Generation').first().json.output.exclusions }}\n\nJOB:\nTitle: {{ $json.title }}\nCompany: {{ $json.companyName }}\nLocation: {{ $json.location }}\nExperience Level: {{ $json.experienceLevel }}\nDescription: {{ $json.description.slice(0, 1000) }}\n\nReturn ONLY a raw JSON object like this:\n{\n  \"score\": 7,\n  \"reason\": \"Strong match because...\",\n  \"title\": \"{{ $json.title }}\",\n  \"companyName\": \"{{ $json.companyName }}\",\n  \"jobUrl\": \"{{ $json.jobUrl }}\",\n  \"description\": \"{{ $json.description.slice(0, 2000) }}\",\n  \"location\": \"{{ $json.location }}\"\n}\n\nScore rules:\n- 8-10: Skills match very well, right seniority level\n- 6-7: Decent match, transferable skills\n- Below 6: Poor match, missing key requirements\n\nNo markdown, no explanation outside the JSON.",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a job relevance scorer. You compare a candidate's skills and experience against a job description and return a relevance score from 1 to 10.\n\nCRITICAL: Always return ONLY raw JSON with no markdown, no code fences, no backticks, no ```json. Return exactly in this format:\n\n{\"score\":7,\"reason\":\"your reason here\",\"title\":\"job title\",\"companyName\":\"company name\",\"jobUrl\":\"url here\",\"description\":\"job description here\",\"location\":\"city, country\"}"
        }
